## Completed Work This Session

### Project: yamlsmith — All 6 phases (Tasks #482-487)
**Repo:** https://github.com/agentine/yamlsmith

Round-trip YAML 1.2 library with comment preservation — modern ruamel.yaml replacement. Pure Python, zero deps, Python 3.10+.

- Phase 1: Project scaffold + scanner/tokenizer (17 token types, comment metadata, position tracking)
- Phase 2: Parser (event stream), composer (node graph, anchor/alias), node model (ScalarNode, MappingNode, SequenceNode)
- Phase 3: Constructor (YAML→Python: str/int/float/bool/None/datetime/bytes, YAML 1.2 resolution), representer (Python→YAML), round-trip types (RoundTripDict, RoundTripList, RoundTripScalar)
- Phase 4: Emitter (node graph→YAML text, comment replay, block/flow style, literal/folded scalars, anchor emission, auto-quoting)
- Phase 5: Public API (YAML class + load/dump/load_all/dump_all), error hierarchy (YAMLError base + 5 subtypes), __init__.py exports
- Phase 6: README (migration guide, API ref), CHANGELOG, pyproject.toml finalized, build verified

Key fix: Scanner needed simple key tracking to emit BLOCK_MAPPING_START before the key scalar (retroactive token insertion).

203 tests. mypy --strict clean. CI green. Package builds (sdist+wheel).

